'''Hangar Bay L44-S3''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|hangar bay]] on the [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star's]] southern hemisphere. It was capable of storing three assault shuttles and at least four landing shuttles. It also had a vehicle lift and two blast doors, two airlock doors, a control room, and several power cell recharge units. Directional markings were also laid on the floor for indication of where to land. It was destroyed during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

